00:18:23.459 --> 00:18:24.579
You've repaid your debt.

00:18:24.580 --> 00:18:26.019
Your ties with her end here.

00:18:26.020 --> 00:18:27.499
Now, you can focus entirely

00:18:27.500 --> 00:18:30.059
on your marriage to the Saintess.

00:18:30.060 --> 00:18:31.938
News just came from Wujing City.

00:18:31.939 --> 00:18:33.458
The city lord's daughter,

00:18:33.459 --> 00:18:34.418
Liluo,

00:18:34.419 --> 00:18:36.458
carries the Wujing Saintess' bloodline.

00:18:36.459 --> 00:18:37.499
In three days,

00:18:37.500 --> 00:18:40.620
you'll go
to Wujing City yourself and confirm it.

00:18:41.340 --> 00:18:43.140
You shall show no further disobedience.

00:18:46.419 --> 00:18:47.539
Yes, Father.

00:18:48.100 --> 00:18:50.099
Don't waste any more time.

00:18:50.100 --> 00:18:53.219
The moment that human girl dies
and her soul's gone,

00:18:53.500 --> 00:18:56.060
reclaim the sigil at once.

00:18:58.419 --> 00:18:59.580
Understood.

